{"type":"message","id":"a63aaf32","parentId":"4de7a3ea","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:09:12.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've created:\n1. A comprehensive documentation file: `openclaw-architecture-deep-dive.md`\n2. Three SVG diagrams with animations:\n   - `openclaw-architecture.svg` - Main architecture diagram\n   - `openclaw-memory-system.svg` - Memory system with hybrid search\n   - `openclaw-connection-lifecycle.svg` - Connection lifecycle\n\nLet me provide the user with a summary and show the diagrams.","thinkingSignature":"60352de265c5eb4620de6d388db0d9e8187b8b00f9e919166e1310c7694e9015"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经深度解读了 OpenClaw 的架构模式和记忆系统，并创建了带有动态效果的 SVG 架构图。\n\n## 📚 创建的文件\n\n### 1. 详细文档\n**`openclaw-architecture-deep-dive.md`** - 包含：\n- 整体架构分层（Chat Apps → Gateway → Clients）\n- Gateway 核心职责与组件\n- 连接生命周期流程\n- 记忆系统详解（双层架构、混合搜索、自动刷新）\n- QMD 实验性后端\n- 会话管理与安全模型\n\n### 2. SVG 动态架构图\n\n| 文件 | 内容 | 动态效果 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| `openclaw-architecture.svg` | 整体架构（Chat Apps → Gateway → Clients → AI Provider） | 数据包流动、组件浮动、发光脉冲 |\n| `openclaw-memory-system.svg` | 记忆系统（记忆源 → 混合搜索 → 工具输出） | 记忆文件浮动、分数流动、搜索脉冲 |\n| `openclaw-connection-lifecycle.svg` | 连接生命周期序列 | 淡入动画、认证流程、协议格式 |\n\n## 🎯 核心要点\n\n**架构模式：**\n- 🦞 **单一 Gateway** - 所有渠道的唯一入口\n- 🔌 **插件化通道** - WhatsApp/Telegram/Discord 等独立管理\n- 🔐 **设备级配对** - 本地自动批准，远程需确认\n\n**记忆系统：**\n- 📝 **双层记忆** - `MEMORY.md`（长期）+ `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`（每日）\n- 🔍 **混合搜索** - Vector 语义 + BM25 关键词 + MMR 多样性 + 时间衰减\n- ⚡ **自动刷新** - Compaction 前静默触发，写入记忆后发送 `NO_REPLY`\n\n这些 SVG 可以在浏览器中打开查看动态效果！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":30736,"output":477,"cacheRead":12885,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44098,"cost":{"input":0.0184416,"output":0.0011447999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0007731,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0203595}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773706146223}}
